== **14. MEMBER REMOVAL FROM PROJECT** ==

Admin -> Odoo : Remove Khalid from\n"Website Redesign" members
activate Odoo
Odoo -> Odoo : project.write({member_ids: ...})
note right of Odoo
  Track removed members:
  old_members - new_members = [Khalid]
  Add Khalid to removed_member_ids
  Khalid's existing tasks remain
end note
Odoo -> DB : UPDATE project_member_rel\n(remove Khalid)
Odoo -> DB : UPDATE project_removed_member_rel\n(add Khalid)
