== **15. PAST DATE ENTRY VALIDATION** ==

Member -> Odoo : Submit task for 5 days ago\n(limit is 3 days)
activate Odoo
Odoo -> Odoo : _check_past_date_limit()
Odoo -> DB : Get config: past_date_limit=3
Odoo -> Odoo : today - task_date = 5 days > 3
Odoo -> Odoo : is_pm_or_admin? No (Member)
Odoo --> Member : **ValidationError:**\n"You can only enter tasks up to\n3 days in the past"
deactivate Odoo

PM -> Odoo : Submit task for 5 days ago\n(on behalf of member)
activate Odoo
Odoo -> Odoo : _check_past_date_limit()
Odoo -> Odoo : is_pm_or_admin? Yes -> Skip check
Odoo -> DB : INSERT task (date=5 days ago)
Odoo -> Odoo : _compute_is_late_entry()\nlate_days=5, is_late_entry=True
Odoo --> PM : Task saved (flagged as late entry)
deactivate Odoo

== **16. ATTACHMENT SIZE VALIDATION** ==

Member -> Odoo : Upload file: 150MB video
activate Odoo
Odoo -> Odoo : _validate_attachment_size()
Odoo -> DB : Get config: max_attachment_size=100
Odoo -> Odoo : 150MB > 100MB limit
Odoo --> Member : **ValidationError:**\n"File exceeds maximum\nsize of 100MB"
