== **22. PROJECT PROGRESS COMPUTATION** ==

note over Odoo, DB
  **Project Progress Auto-Update Flow:**
  1. Task approved -> triggers @api.depends('task_ids.approval_status')
  2. _compute_total_logged_hours(): sum of approved tasks' duration
  3. _compute_progress_percentage(): (logged / expected) * 100
  4. _compute_task_stats(): total tasks + pending count

  Example: "Website Redesign" (200 expected hours)
  - 15 approved tasks, total 45 approved hours
  - Progress = 45/200 * 100 = 22.5%
  - Pending tasks: 4
end note

== **23. SECURITY & ACCESS CONTROL** ==

note over Member, Admin
  **Three Security Groups (Hierarchical):**
  - **group_member**: See own tasks only, create tasks in assigned projects
  - **group_project_manager** (inherits member): See all tasks in managed projects, approve/reject, run reports
  - **group_admin_manager** (inherits PM): Full access to everything, configure settings, archive/restore

  **13 Record Rules enforce:**
  - Members: read/write own tasks only
  - PMs: read all tasks in managed projects, write approval fields
  - Admins: unrestricted CRUD on all models
  - Archived projects: visible only to admins
end note

@enduml
